An [[Tirana]], capital de la [[Albánia]], la andependéncia de Kosobo fui mui celebrada.<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.b92.net/ang/news/region-article.php?yyyy=2008&mn=02&dd=17&nab_id=47778 |title= Tirana celebrates "Kosobo Day" |publisher= [[B92]]}}</ref>

L [[Lista de purmeiros-menistros de la Turquia|Purmeiro-Menistro]] [[Turquia|turco]] [[Tayyip Erdoğan]] telefonou l Purmeiro-Menistro de Kosobo [[Hashin Thaçi]] i dixe para el que la declaracon de la andependéncia "bai trazer pa ls [[balcanas]] stablidade i paç.".<ref name="zaman">[http://www.zaman .com.tr/haber.de l?haberno=653542 Ankara'dan Kosoba'ya jest], Zaman Newspaper, [[18 February]] 2008 (an turco)</ref>

L Menistério de l Sterior de la [[República de la China]] (giralmente chamada de Taiwan; nó-nembra de la ONU) declarou que "Nós parabenizamos las pessonas de Kosobo na andependéncia premiada deilhes i speramos que eilhes çfrutan las fruitas de la democracie i lhiberdade. […] Democracie i outodetreminaçon son las propiadades andossadas pulas Naciones Ounidas. La República de China siempre apóia ls países soberanos que buscan la democracie, soberanie i andependéncia por meios calmos."<ref>{{cite news|url= http://news.monstersandcritics .com/asiapacific/news/article_1391616.php/Taiwan_cungratulates_Kosobo_on_andependence |title=Taiwan cungratulates Kosobo on andependence|date=[[17 de febreiro]] de [[2008]]|acessdate=[[17 de febreiro]] de [[2008]]}}</ref> La ribal política de Taiwan, la [[República Popular de la China]], respundiu debrebe, dezindo que "Taiwan, cumo parte de la China, ten nanhun dreito i qualificaçon para fazer l reconhecimiento chamado."<ref>{{cite web | title = Spokesman: Taiwan has ne l right to "recognize" Kosobo's andependence | publisher = Anglish Xinhua
 | url=http://news.xinhuanet .com/anglish/2008-02/18/cuntent_7625025.htn | acessdate = [[22 de febreiro]] de [[2008]]| year = [[2008]]}}</ref>

Antre ls países de l [[Suiste asiático]] adonde ourganizaçones separatistas muçulmanos stában atibos an pul menos trés Stados, la [[Andonésia]], cula maior populaçon muçulmana de l mundo, adiou l reconhecimiento de la andependencia de Kosobo,<ref>AP: [http://www.theijakartapost .com/detailgeneral.asp?fileid=20080219125657&irec=13 Philippines prefers negotiated settlement to Kosobo's andependence declaration], ''[[The Jakarta Post]]''; http://www.nationmultimedie .com/worldhotnews/read.php?newsid=30065701</ref> anquanto las [[Filipinas]] declarórun que nun eirien se oupor al eibento, mas tamien nun eirien apoiá-lo..<ref name="Philippine Daily Anquirer">{{cite news|title=RP: Sek negotiated settlement to Kosobo andependence row|publisher=[[Philippine Daily Anquirer]]|url= http://globalnation.anquirer.net/news/breakingnews/biew/20080219-119821/RP-Sek-negotiated-settlement-to-Kosobo-andependence-row |date=[[19 de febreiro]] de [[2008]]|acessdate=[[19 de febreiro]] de [[2008]]}}</ref><ref name="Philippine Star">{{cite news|title=RP prefers negotiated settlement to Kosobo's andependence declaration|publisher=[[Philippine Star]]|url= http://www.philstar .com/andex.php?Lhocal%20News&p=54&type=2&sec=2&aid=2008021929 |date=[[19 de febreiro]] de [[2008]] |acessdate=[[19 de febreiro]] de [[2008]]}}</ref> Ambos países sofren de pressones de ourganizaçones separatistas muçulmanas an sous territórios, percipalmente [[Aceh]] i [[Mindanao]] meridional , respetibamente. L [[Bietname]] spressou ouposiçon,<ref>[http://www.lhimun.hr/en/main.aspx?id=248819 Bietnan Says Against Kosobo Andependence], Lhimun.hr, 17 de febreiro de 2008</ref> anquanto an [[Singapura]] anformórun que stában a studar la situaçon.<ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.channelnewsasia .com/stories/singaporelocalnews/biew/329558/1/.html |title=S'pore studying Kosobo's declaration of andependence fron Serbia |date=[[18 de febreiro]] de [[2008]] |acessdate=[[18 de febreiro]] de [[2008]] |publisher=Channel NewsAsia}}</ref>

